cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is about video super-resolution using convolutional neural networks and motion compensation. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image and video processing. The second likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with video processing. The third likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper uses deep learning techniques. The fourth likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with intelligent systems for video processing. The fifth likely category is cs.GR (Graphics) as the paper deals with image and video rendering.
